<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="min-vh-100 m-0">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" href="img/logo.png" />
    <title>Mappa Parcheggi</title>

    <!-- JQuery-->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.js" integrity="sha256-2Kok7MbOyxpgUVvAk/HJ2jigOSYS2auK4Pfzbm7uH60="
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <!-- Bootstrap-->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
    integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.1.1/css/all.min.css">
    <script src="scriptMap.js" defer></script>
</head>
<body class="min-vh-100 d-flex flex-column">
    <%- include('header.ejs', {logged: logged}) %>

    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center position-absolute">
      <input class="form-control w-25 mt-3 border border-dark" id="searchTextField" type="text" size="50" style="border-radius: 1rem;" placeholder="Cerca qui">
    </div>
    
    <div id="map" class="w-100 h-75 flex-grow-1"></div>

    <div class="d-flex flex-row-reverse">
    <img class="mt-2" src="img/powered_by_google_on_white.png" width="100vw" alt="Powered by Google">
    </div>
    <small class=" mx-auto text-center">I parcheggi mostrati su questa mappa sono soltanto quelli con inserzioni disponibili per la prenotazione.<br>
    Non trovi il tuo parcheggio? Prova a creare un'inserzione ed unisciti agli utenti di Parket!</small>
    <script
      src="https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/js?key=AIzaSyDU3e_OE0se9mggt7FEAoqg8Zoye4xuxIk&callback=initMap&v=weekly&libraries=places"
      defer
    ></script>
    
    <%- include('footer.ejs', {logged: logged}) %>
</body>
</html>